snippet.title: Elon Musks first wife describes their relationship
snippet.description:
#relationshipadvice #relationshipadvocates
JUSTINE MUSKS BOOKS:-

A Flighted Friend (2020) https://amzn.to/3fCIZtv
Lord of Bones (2008) https://amzn.to/3AgUHSg
Uninvited (2007) https://amzn.to/3fAGQyx
Blood Angel (2005)  https://amzn.to/3jmIB3g

Elon Musk Books:-

Elon Musk: How the Billionaire CEO of SpaceX and Tesla is Shaping our Future: https://amzn.to/3fyT8qW



ELONS REPONSE TO THIS VIDEO: https://youtu.be/-IFO-ce7V3M
ELONS VIEW OF LOVE AND RELATIONSHIPS: https://youtu.be/yGQVR6Fojko
ELONS FIRST WIFE DESCRIBES WHAT IT TAKE TO BE HIM: https://youtu.be/CVjQ-Jhnu2k

Please watch all three videos before you judge Elon.


Elon Musks first wife describes their relationship

The purpose of this video is NOT TO DISPARAGE ELON. I LOVE ELON DEEPLY. The purpose of this video is to highlight to people that money and intelligence quite literally does not ensure a good intimate relationship. Few of us will be able to achieve what Elon has achieved. To sacrifice ones intimate relationship, the most important relationship you will have in your life, for the HOPE! of money and success is wrong. And not a decision you should take lightly. Nothing should take precedence over loving your partner. Whatever time you have left over should be spent on changing the world.
